## Security Measures Implemented

### Configuration Security ✅
- Environment variable support
- No hardcoded credentials
- Secure session settings
- HTTPS enforcement

### API Security ✅
- JWT authentication
- Bearer token validation
- CORS restrictions
- Security headers (XSS, nosniff, frame options)
- Input validation ready

### File Security ✅
- .htaccess protection for sensitive files
- Proper file permissions documented
- Private directory outside web root
- Directory browsing disabled

### Password Security ✅
- Bcrypt hashing (built into Gibbon)
- Strong password policies
- Password change requirements documented

