## Performance Considerations

### Shared Hosting Optimizations
- Database-backed sessions (no file permission issues)
- Optimized autoloader (--optimize-autoloader)
- Production-mode dependencies (--no-dev)
- Caching configuration ready

### Scalability
- Pagination on student lists
- API rate limiting ready
- Database query optimization (built into Gibbon)
- CDN-ready static assets

---

## Maintenance & Support

### Automated Backups
**Cron Job Template Provided**:
```bash
# Daily database backup at 2 AM
0 2 * * * mysqldump -u user -p database | gzip > backup_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql.gz
```

### Monitoring
**Log Files**:
- Application errors: `/private/logs/gibbon_errors.log`
- Access logs: Hostinger control panel
- API logs: Built into error logging

### Update Path
**Gibbon Updates**:
- Regular security patches available
- Community support active
- Documentation: https://docs.gibbonedu.org/

---

## Technical Specifications

### Requirements Met

| Component | Required | Provided |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| PHP | 8.0+ | ✅ 8.1/8.2 compatible |
| MySQL | 5.7+ | ✅ 8.0 compatible |
| Extensions | curl, intl, mbstring, etc. | ✅ All documented |
| Composer | Latest | ✅ Dependencies listed |
| Web Server | Apache | ✅ .htaccess configured |

### File Sizes
- Gibbon core: ~50MB (unpacked)
- Database schema: 521KB SQL
- Deployment package: ~30-40MB (zipped)

### Database Schema
- Tables: 100+ tables
- Default users: Admin account included
- Demo data: Available (gibbon_demo.sql)

---

## Known Limitations

### Current State
- ⚠️ Local testing not performed yet (recommended before deployment)
- ⚠️ SMTP not configured (needs user credentials)
- ⚠️ API endpoints are basic (expand as needed)
- ⚠️ No real-time features (websockets not included)

### Shared Hosting Constraints
- Limited PHP memory (256MB configured)
- No shell access for some hosts
- Execution time limits (300s configured)
- File upload size limits (20MB configured)

### Future Enhancements
- Additional API endpoints as needed
- Real-time notifications (when scaling to VPS)
- Advanced reporting features
- Mobile app integration (API ready)

